Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:09.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,惨敗　沼攻略に挑んだ坂崎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:07.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:13.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In his short time challenging the Bog, Sakazaki has lost 43,520,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:14.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２時間足らずで4352万を失う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But! But!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:17.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが しかしカイジの脳裏に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:19.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Inspiration flashes through Kaiji's brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:19.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひらめき　閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:26.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)\pos(640,505)}The Clue to Beating the Bog
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:29.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん！おっちゃん\Nビッグニュースだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Big news, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:31.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can do this! I've got it figured out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:32.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いける　いけるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:35.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:44.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops... Did they take you away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:44.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん　さらわれちまったか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:49.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？手紙？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:49.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:58.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　五里霧中　四面楚歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:58.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji. I'm completely bewildered. Surrounded by foes. {this scene will never work in english. silly lack of 4ccs.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:02.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,孤城落日　油断大敵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:02.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Completely alone, betrayed by my overconfidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:06.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我 今 生涯における絶対的 窮地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:06.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm in the worst pinch of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:09.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶句舌根　死屍累々
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:11.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At the end of my rope! Surrounded by corpses! In the depths of pandemonium!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:12.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿鼻叫喚　破天破漢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:13.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Heaven's fall, man's fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:18.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,されど 我 いまだ死なず
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.46,0:01:18.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I'm not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:23.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,光明あり\N我 その光明に向かい突き進む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:23.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's a light at the end of the tunnel, and I'm going to keep chasing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:26.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,慙愧苦渋　悪戦苦闘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:29.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The shame, the bitterness, the long odds... I can go beyond them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな過去は断ち切った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:33.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの悪魔 怪物への復讐は済んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:33.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is my revenge on that devil, that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:35.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が手によって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,By my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:39.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？我が手によって？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:38.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,By his own hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:43.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ これやったの\Nおっちゃんかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:40.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So he...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:43.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He did this himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:46.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我 今や明鏡止水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:46.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My mind is as clear as a mirror, as still as a pool of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:52.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Body and soul are cleansed! My rage, my tears, all fade like the mist before the morning sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:52.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心身浄化　怒りも悔いも\N全て雲散霧消
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:55.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Like clouds before the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:56.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,風に散った塵のごとし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:02:02.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは ただ３日後に迫った\N決戦に集中するのみ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:02:02.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All that remains is to focus on the battle which occurs in three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:05.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,果たす 乾坤一擲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:06.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I risk it all to be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:10.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,起死回生　的中を！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:08.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:13.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,的中ってまさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A lock... Wait, he can't—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:18.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,競馬で残った金を\N6000万にすれば やり直せる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:18.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we just play the ponies and get back up to 60 mil, we can try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:24.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああもう！バカバカバカ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:25.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez! You moron! {welp, i guess kaiji is a moe anime.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:28.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,馬なんか当たらねえって\N言っただろ バカ！バカ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:27.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stupid! There's no way you're gonna win on horses like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:30.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You dumbass! —Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:32.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アイテ！もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:32.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:40.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！そうか その手があったか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:39.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I get it! That's how it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:43.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待てよ　ひょっとすると
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:43.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:47.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can make it past the second barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:47.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できるかもしれねえ\N第２関門突破も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:57.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So the only problem is those devilish triple trays...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:55.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となれば 問題は３つ目のあの悪魔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段クルーン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:03.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ　ネタには たどり着いてるが\N肝心の攻略法が…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:03.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can get there often enough, but if we don't figure out how to beat that part...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:07.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:08.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ クソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:14.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうしてる間にも\N刻々と俺の貴重な時間がなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:14.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And while I'm wasting time with this, my time's ticking down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちくしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:20.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジに残された\Nシャバでの滞在日数は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:23.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Counting today, Kaiji has only eight days left on the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:23.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この日を入れて あと８日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:31.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２時間も ああしてるんですよ\N今日も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:30.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's been doing that for two hours just today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:33.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's trying to work out some trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,細工する気かもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何らかの方法で沼に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Some way to beat the Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:38.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？\N奴も必死だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's got a lot riding on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:42.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をしてくるか分からん\N隠しカメラを設置しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he might try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Set up the hidden cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,監視カメラの他にですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not just the security cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:46.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,念には念を入れてな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Better safe than sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では早速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll get right on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't let a single ant creep in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アリ１匹 通すものか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,潰すんだ　わずかな可能性も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll snuff out even his faintest hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:06.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なす術なし　あの沼攻略は夢物語
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't think of a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:06.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Beating the Bog is a pipe dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:09.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あり得ない絵空事なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:09.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An impossible fantasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:23.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ところが 涼を求めて入った喫茶店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:23.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The scene, a café he entered to cool off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:31.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Man, that's loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:34.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How long have they been working on that building, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マスター　向かいのビル\N建って だいぶ経つよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かれこれ１年かな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's been about a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:38.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ工事 終わらないんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And they're still not done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:42.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがさ この間の…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:41.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:46.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思いもしない情報を得る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji has an unexpected realization!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:49.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji immediately confirms this with a builder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:49.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早速 カイジは\Nそのことを工事関係者に確かめる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ そうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:51.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:53.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:05:00.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった　何てことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Would you look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:05.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残っていやがった\N俺にも ツキ 運が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:05.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I still have a chance! Luck's still on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:12.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この糸を離すな　登るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't let go of this thread!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll climb it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:16.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この天恵をたどり 地上まで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This revelation will lead me back to the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:19.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄を抜けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can make it out of that hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:23.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That devilish, impossible triple tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:23.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの悪魔 難攻不落の３段クルーン
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can smash right through it, and make it pay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:30.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの壁を突き崩し\N全て吐き出させる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６億 ７億
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:36.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,600 million! No, 700 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:39.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:43.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり いねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:42.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need you here, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃんの力が\N必要だっていうのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:51.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夏は地方に行ってるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They race out in the sticks in summer, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:54.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小倉 札幌 新潟… どこだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:55.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kokura? Sapporo? Niigata? Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃんは どこへ向かった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Where did he head off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:06:02.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,場外では買わないはずだ\N何しろ 一世一代の大勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:59.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He has to be playing at the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:02.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be the bet of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのヒロイックなおっちゃんが\N馬場へ行かないなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:06.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Someone with a hero complex like his is definitely gonna go to the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:07.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:11.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これか ひょっとして…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:30.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,８レース ２番単勝に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Race 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,#2 to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:34.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ろ… 600万！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:33.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Six million!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？\N何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Six million!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:39.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,600万？\Nよろしいんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:45.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:51.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't if you don't let go of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:51.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってってくれって\Nあんたが手 離さなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,も… 持ってって…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You need to let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから… あんたが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:07:00.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんですか？本当に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:59.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure about this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:02.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:06.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よくない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:03.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:08.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:08.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:16.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry. He can't bet that money. We're taking it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:15.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すいません\Nそれ 手つけちゃいけない金なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:18.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,返してください\Nな… 何を言う！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:19.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about!? This is my—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これはわしの…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金庫から\Nくすねてきた金だろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the money you snatched out of the safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:27.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ！何を言う！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, you idiot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:29.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうわけなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So really, he can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:36.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ おい　こら待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:33.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってってカイジ！\Nきたら どうするつもりだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:42.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,11倍 6600万だぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's paying 11-to-1! I'll end up with 66 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:46.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こねえよ！\N単勝２番 ミココノチカラ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:46.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me? #2, Mikoko's Might, to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:50.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな調子よく\N娘の名前の馬がきたりしねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This isn't some movie or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna win it all betting on a horse with your daughter's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:54.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ　それだけじゃない\Nそれだけじゃないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:54.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You moron! That's not all there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:58.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見ろ これを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at the jockey's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:01.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騎手の名前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,木崎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:02.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Miranda?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:08.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか　ミココノチカラに加えて\N騎手の名前が木崎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:08.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The horse's named Mikoko's Might, and the jockey's named Miranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:13.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,木崎… きざき… きざき\Nきさき… きさき
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:15.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Miranda... Miranda... Miranda... Miranda... Miranda... Miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:16.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奇跡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この符合をどう取る？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:18.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This can't just be a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:20.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:23.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:27.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いて損した　くるわけねえだろ\Nそんな語呂合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't even wanna hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not a sure win, that's just a bad pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジ君　そう言うけど\Nないんだぞ？こんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:32.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's not like that, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:35.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君\Nおおっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:39.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第８レース 発売を締め切りました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:39.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Betting for the eighth race is now closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:46.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何てことを…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:51.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What have you done!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何てことをしてくれたんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:55.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恨むぞ　わしは君を一生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:55.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hate you for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:01.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,#9, Hattori King, wins. #7, Mitsuki Sun, places.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:09:02.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１着 ９番ハットリキング\N２着 ７番ミツキタイヨウ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,#1, Rinna Mizuho, places.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:06.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３着 １番リンナミズホ\Nしんがり12着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:08.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Coming last, in twelfth, is #2, Mikoko's Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:10.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２番ミココノチカラ\N繰り返します　１着…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:12.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Repeating. #9, Hattori King, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:13.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかった\Nね？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:12.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,—Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,#7, Mitsuki Sun, places.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:23.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたらいい\Nわしは これから先
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do I do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:23.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's next for me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奇跡なんて望むな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:25.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't just wait for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:29.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つってことは\Nそんな神頼みなんかじゃなく
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:29.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Winning doesn't happen because you just get lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:32.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,具体的な勝算のかなたにある\N現実だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:32.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It comes from the odds being on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つべくして勝つ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You win because you must!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:36.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと言っても…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:40.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I figured out how to beat the Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:40.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思いついたんだ　沼攻略を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:43.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Beat the Bog!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼攻略？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:57.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:56.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何せ おっちゃんは\N元土建屋だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:00.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You used to work in construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You think it'll work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その経験からして この話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:05.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカげてる\Nおっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:06.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカげてる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:09.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But! But!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:12.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だがしかし 天才的な発想だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's pure genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:14.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけるかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It just might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:19.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか\Nだが かかるぞ それ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:19.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's gonna take some serious cash, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:23.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Between the trick itself and the bet, six million isn't gonna cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:24.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕掛けがねえと 勝負金\Nとても600万じゃ足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:27.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金だけでなく\Nそれなりの人手も必要だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:27.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Money isn't the only problem. We'll need a helping hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything to lose, so I'm gonna give this one guy a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:31.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメ元で\Nまず当たってみたいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:33.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？当たる？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give him a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:37.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　できることなら\N引き入れたい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:37.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I want to get him in on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:46.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 大した金にはならないが\Nもらっていくか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:46.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not too much money. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:49.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:49.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ とりあえず今日は\Nこれで帰りますが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:53.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But next time, I want cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:53.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くれぐれも次は\N現金でお願いしますよ 遠藤さん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:57.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you don't pay up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 払えなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:01.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, you know what Teiai does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帝愛の掟に従ってもらいますがね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:14.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:17.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪徳金融も\Nそれなりに大変なんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:17.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So the loan shark's hoisted with his own petard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:19.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who's there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:25.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Endoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,久しぶりですね 遠藤さん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おおっ カイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでお前が…\Nちょっと事情がありましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:34.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Things happened. I'm out on furlough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:34.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一時的に出してもらったんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:39.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,儲け話があるんですよ\N成功すれば約７億
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:39.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I know a way we can both get rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:42.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？\N遠藤さんも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:44.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I can pull this off, I stand to make 700 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:45.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帝愛の人間だから\N聞いたことあるでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帝愛の裏カジノの\N沼という異名のパチンコ台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:49.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You know the Bog, right? The pachinko machine in one of Teiai's illegal casinos?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The one they call the Man-Eater?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:55.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人食いモンスターが\Nあるということ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:58.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've figured out how to beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:58.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつを攻略する算段が\Nつきました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:01.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,攻略？あの1000倍台をか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Beat it? Beat the thousand-rate machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:05.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ\Nバカな　不可能だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:02.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:05.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way. That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいえ　できます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:07.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No. I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:12.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We{\i0} can do it. You and me, Endoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:12.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と遠藤さん\N２人が力を合わせれば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:20.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に できたとしても…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if you can pull it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフ　気が引けますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What, feeling shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:26.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't wanna cause trouble for your higher-ups in Teiai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:26.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボスである帝愛に\N弓は引けないってことですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:33.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ そいつは立派というか\N何というか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:33.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You think honor matters like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:38.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you don't pay back that loan you took out....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:38.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき取り立てられた借金\N返せなかったら 俺たちと同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:41.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地下行きでしょ 遠藤さんも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:41.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're going underground just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:46.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違いますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:57.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夢みてえなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you just dream that shit up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:00.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It ain't gonna be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:13:01.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな　甘くねえぞ 勝負は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:04.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You really think everything's gonna go according to plan like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:04.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな机上の理論どおり\N事が運ぶと思ってんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Something's going to happen that you didn't plan for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:07.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不測の事態は常に起こり得る
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One little slip-up and you're bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:11.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つ何かが かみ合わなきゃ\Nそれで破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,End of story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:15.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しまいだ　軟弱なんだよ その計画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:15.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This plan of yours is trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:26.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ ひいき目に見て\N成功する確率は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:28.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess if I wanted to be generous I'd say you've got half a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:31.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,半分てとこだろう\N半分？５割ってことですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Half!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fifty-fifty, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:39.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ　上等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:43.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５割上等！十分じゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fifty-fifty's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I don't do anything, I'm gonna keep falling behind until you fall into the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:46.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ 何もしなきゃ\Nジリ貧で地獄行きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:49.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の この現状を考えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:51.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A fifty-fifty chance at 700 million at this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５割で７億！\N運命を託すのに十分な確率
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:54.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's enough to risk my fate on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And aren't you in the same boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:58.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは同じはずだ 遠藤さんも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チッ ガキが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:07.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:13.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ野郎 言ってみろ！\Nいくら必要なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:12.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, you shithead! Tell me how much you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:18.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd ask. I need 50 mil for pachinko balls, day-of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:19.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが遠藤さん\N当日のパチンコ代 5000万
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:23.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And five up front for the prep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:23.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それと勝負前の工作費として\N即金で今 500万
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:25.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プラス 人　こういう裏ごとに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:28.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus manpower. I need a few guys who aren't afraid to get their hands dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:29.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,躊躇なく\N手を染めてくれる人を数人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この金と人を\N遠藤さんに用意してもらいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need you to come up with the cash and the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう\Nそうこなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:37.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Great, I couldn't do it—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:40.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし３羽ガラスだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But! Three crows!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Three... Crows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:43.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３羽ガラス？\Nああ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:45.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They use to call loans where the interest was ten percent
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,朝 カラスがカアと鳴けば\N借りた金に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:49.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１割の金利がつく借金を\Nカラス金っていうんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:49.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,at the crow's first caw in the morning "crow money".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:53.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回はそれが３羽で１日３割
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:53.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I want three times that. Thirty percent a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:58.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pay it back within a day, and you pay thirty percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:58.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借りた時から24時間以内に返せば\N３割増しで済むが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１分でも過ぎれば\Nその３割増した金に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:05.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But a second later, and you pay another thirty percent on the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:05.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再び金利が乗り さらに３割増し
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Compound interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:07.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,複利で増える
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:11.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回の場合 当日の勝負金5000万は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:14.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The fifty million you want is just gonna be sixty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:14.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単純に３割増しで6500万だが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:19.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But you're paying compound interest on the five you want today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:19.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が今日 不足金で借りたいと\N言っていた500万は複利で増える
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:22.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに工作費そのものは500万でも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus, you say you want five million,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:30.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but it'll cost me another five million to hire the labor you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちが人手を用意するなら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:31.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その人件費および 人材調達の\N手間賃として もう500万が必要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:36.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり お前が今日\N俺から借りる金は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:31.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Today, you're borrowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:39.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:37.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ten million.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が指定した勝負日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:46.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thirty percent compound interest over the six days until you go for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:46.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６日後まで１日３割の複利で\N増えていくとなると
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Adds up to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:48.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうなる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,48.26 million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,4826万8090
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And 8,090?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:55.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,端数は まけてやってもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll round it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:59.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！ひでえ商売だな相変わらず
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're just as much of a ballbuster as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:04.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を言う！俺だって\Nこいつは裏金融からの借り受け
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:04.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's your problem!? I'm gonna have to borrow to come up with this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:07.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you fuck this up, I'm a dead man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:07.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この計画が破綻したら\N同時に俺も破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,首を つらなきゃならねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to hang myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:13.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに それをこんな一か八かに\N貸し付けてんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:13.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I'm still sticking my neck out for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:17.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感謝されることがあっても\N文句など言われる筋合いはない！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:17.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You should be thanking me, not bitching!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:21.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった　分かりましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:21.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:25.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So sixty-five mil for the fifty day-of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:25.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってことは当日の5000万が6500万
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,工作費の1000万が約4800万で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:28.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And forty-eight for the construction...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:32.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１億1300万にして返すってことか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:31.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll owe you 130 million, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:36.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プラス ７億の出玉を２人で折半だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:36.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus we split the 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:39.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:38.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:42.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be in this just as deep as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:42.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然だろ　共犯者なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:47.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The interest is just for my services.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:47.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきの貸し付け うんぬんて話は\Nあくまで金融業者としての請求だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:52.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,共犯者としての取り分\N成功報酬は別だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:52.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't include what I get for going in on this plan with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:58.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So wait, wait, 350 plus the interest... You want 463 million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:55.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３億5000万に さっきのを合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:58.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４億6300万も持ってくってのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:01.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's almost two-thirds of the payout!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,７億の ほぼ３分の２じゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:05.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ仕方ないな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:08.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fair's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:08.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,公平に分配すると\Nそうなるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:12.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No fucking way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あきまへん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけたら あきまへん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's bullshit! No fucking way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:21.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あかん あかん あかん\Nふざけたら あかん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:20.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way! No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:21.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's bullshit! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん　落ち着けって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:28.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's just too greedy! Fuck that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:28.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強欲や　それは あまりに強欲\Nふざけたら あきまへん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:32.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何なんだ？この薄汚ねえオヤジは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:32.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's up with this dirty old guy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何やと！\Nおっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:34.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:36.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいから落ち着けって\N話はこれからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We haven't even talked it over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:40.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't need to pick a fight with him straight off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを 最初からケンカ腰で\Nどうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:44.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間だろ？俺たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're all in this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:47.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間？\Nそうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:45.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:53.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼攻略の厚い壁は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:55.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Us three are gonna bust through that Bog standing in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この３人で突破する
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:05.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:07.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:17.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これにサインしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:22.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,即金500万　３羽ガラスの借用書だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:20.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a Three Crow loan contract for five million.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:29.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In the end, they arrive on splitting the profit from the winnings three ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 ３人の成功報酬は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:30.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,均等に純利益の\N３等分ということで決着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:34.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に出玉が７億1300万だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:34.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If the Bog pays out 713 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:39.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤に支払う経費と金利が\N１億1300万だとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:39.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And Endoh's loans add up to 113 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:44.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,７億1300万から それを引き\N残った６億を２億ずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:44.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Each of them takes 200 million from the 600 left over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:47.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,均等に分けようという\N取り決めである
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They settle on an even split!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？不満か？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What, not satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:54.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　この男 油断ならねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:50.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:54.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can't let down your guard around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:57.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take a good close look at the interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:58.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特に金利だけは\Nよくよく見ておかねえと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:02.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ　こんな場面でハメて\Nどうする
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:01.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot! I'm not going to sneak anything in now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:04.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪徳金融が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:04.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're a loan shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:14.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金は？\N500万なら とりあえず 今ある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Where's the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:14.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you just need five million, I've got it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:24.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　ほら500万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:21.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is it. Five million.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:28.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's do this, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:28.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　おっちゃん やるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:32.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤さんの本番は もう少し先だが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:34.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endoh has some time to wait. but we make our move tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは今夜 動く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:39.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっとる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:37.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:43.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっとる…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:46.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The man known as Sakazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:46.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男 坂崎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:52.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Goes as wild as he ever will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:52.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一世一代の大暴れ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やる　開くんや
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can do it! It's opening up in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:03.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The path opens up in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:03.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず わしが道を開く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼むぜ　おっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:11.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失敗は許されない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Failure is not an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:16.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The bell sounds on round two! The chance for a miraculous comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:16.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆転勝利への奇跡\N第２ラウンドのゴングが鳴る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鳴る！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:17.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It rings forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:20.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{ed}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:26.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Proverbs of Kaiji Returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:33.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't just wait for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:39.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Winning doesn't happen because you just get lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:45.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It comes from the odds being on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:53.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You win because you must!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm Kaiji's first editor, Ikoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:59.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm the third editor, Nishimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:00.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm the fifth editor, Tsunakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:04.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Our release of Kaiji paperbacks for convenience stores is on sale now!
